                            {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Seek",
                                "alt": "Seek",
                                "game-obj": "Actions",
                                "aonid": 2301
                            }
                        ],
                        "text": "The giant badger enters a state of pure rage that lasts for 1 minute, until there are no enemies it can perceive, or until it falls unconscious, whichever comes first. While raging, the giant badger has AC 17, its jaws Strike deals 1d8+8 damage, and its claw Strike deals 1d6+6 damage. While raging, the giant badger also can't use actions that have the concentrate trait except for Seek. After it has stopped raging, a giant badger can't use Badger Rage again for 1 minute."
